block content
  include _includes/main-menu.jade
  .section
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h1 Getting Started
          h4 Spin up a node on the bitcoin network.
          p Bitcore is kind of like express but for bitcoin servers. Each bitcoin node will be full capable of monitoring the network, making transactions, and storing the blockchain..
        .col-sm-6
          p Image goes here

      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h4 Install Bitcore
          p First install bitcore and then do some stuff
        .col-sm-6
          pre npm install -g bitcore

      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h4 Create a node
          p We are going to create a bitcore node here and call it <kbd>mynode</kbd>
        .col-sm-6
          pre bitcore create mynode <br />cd mynode
          
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h4 Add a service
          p Install both the insight UI and the insight API full featured block exploreres.
        .col-sm-6
          pre bitcore add insight-api insight-ui

      .row
        .col-sm-6
          h4 Start your node
          p First install bitcore and the do some stuff.
        .col-sm-6
          pre bitcore start

